.TH HYPRWAYLAND\-SCANNER 1 "2025-10-30" "hyprwayland-scanner 0.4.5" "Hyprland Ecosystem"
.SH NAME
hyprwayland\-scanner \- generate C++ bindings from Wayland protocol XML files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyprwayland\-scanner
.RI [ options ]
.I protopath
.I outpath
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyprwayland\-scanner
is a Hyprland implementation of wayland\-scanner that generates RAII\-ready,
modern C++ bindings for Wayland protocols.
It can generate code for either server\-side or client\-side protocol
implementations.
.PP
Requires a C++ compiler with C++23 support.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.I protopath
Path to the input Wayland protocol XML file.
.TP
.I outpath
Output directory for the generated C++ source files.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Display version information and exit.
.TP
.BR \-c ", " \-\-client
Generate client\-side code.
The default is to generate server\-side code.
.TP
.B \-\-no\-interfaces
Exclude interface definitions from the generated output.
.TP
.B \-\-wayland\-enums
Use Wayland\-style enum naming (snake_case instead of camelCase).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wayland\-scanner (1),
.BR Hyprland (1)
.SH AUTHOR
The Hyprland Development Team
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at
.UR https://github.com/hyprwm/hyprwayland-scanner/issues
.UE .
